_______________________________________________________________________________
"Dream Reality"   
        Using this power, the mentalist is able to enter his own
        dream world.  Once within the world, he can manipulate
        it to suit his own tastes.  (Type 'realityhelp' within
        the reality for more information.)  He can also invite
        others into his dream.  Be warned that travel between
        the dream reality and the 'real' reality is very
        draining spiritually.

        NOTE:  This IS a dream.  You may not give objects to others,
        and objects that are dropped are lost forever in the
        primeval Dreamscape.
 
SP Cost:  variable	Guild Level:  8	Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  dreamr
